CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS research_innovation.scientific_inquiry_implementation ( inquiry_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, curiosity_approach TEXT, communication_plan TEXT, collaboration_guideline TEXT, hypothesis_development TEXT, experiment_framework TEXT, execution_plan TEXT, observation_time TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, investigator_id INTEGER, project_identifier VARCHAR(20), financial_support TEXT, ethics_clearance BOOLEAN, participant_count INTEGER, certainty_level DECIMAL(5,2), error_margin DECIMAL(5,2), analysis_method TEXT, review_status TEXT, journal_name TEXT, references_count INTEGER DEFAULT 0, application_practical TEXT, future_investigation_directions TEXT ); INSERT INTO research_innovation.scientific_inquiry_implementation ( curiosity_approach, communication_plan, collaboration_guideline, hypothesis_development, experiment_framework, execution_plan, investigator_id, project_identifier, financial_support, ethics_clearance, participant_count, certainty_level, error_margin, analysis_method, review_status, journal_name, application_practical, future_investigation_directions ) VALUES ( 'Exploring the effects of dark matter on galactic rotation curves', 'Presenting findings at the Astrophysics Symposium', 'Collaboration with NASA and European Space Agency', 'Dark matter influences galactic dynamics significantly', 'Double-blind randomized observational study', 'Utilizing state-of-the-art telescopes and sensors', 1056, 'DMG-2024-042', 'International Space Research Fund #8976543', TRUE, 10000, 97.50, 1.75, 'Linear regression with robust error variance', 'Under Peer Review', 'Astrophysical Journal', 'Insights into galaxy formation and evolution', 'Study the impact of dark matter on black hole growth' ); CREATE INDEX idx_inquiry_investigator ON research_innovation.scientific_inquiry_implementation(investigator_id); CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW research_innovation.active_inquiries AS SELECT inquiry_id, curiosity_approach, collaboration_guideline, hypothesis_development, investigator_id, project_identifier, observation_time FROM research_innovation.scientific_inquiry_implementation WHERE review_status IN ('Under Peer Review', 'Accepted') AND observation_time >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 year'; CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION increment_references_count() RETURNS TRIGGER AS $$ BEGIN NEW.references_count = OLD.references_count + 1; RETURN NEW; END; $$ LANGUAGE plpgsql; CREATE TRIGGER update_references_count BEFORE UPDATE OF references_count ON research_innovation.scientific_inquiry_implementation FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION increment_references_count(); UPDATE research_innovation.scientific_inquiry_implementation SET references_count = references_count WHERE inquiry_id = (SELECT MAX(inquiry_id) FROM research_innovation.scientific_inquiry_implementation); ANALYZE research_innovation.scientific_inquiry_implementation;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS research_methodology.scientific_method_application ( method_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, curiosity_driven_approach TEXT, communication_strategy TEXT, collaboration_principle TEXT, hypothesis_formulation TEXT, experimental_design TEXT, implementation_process TEXT, observation_date TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, researcher_id INTEGER, project_code VARCHAR(20), funding_source VARCHAR(100), ethical_approval_status BOOLEAN, sample_size INTEGER, confidence_level DECIMAL(5,2), margin_of_error DECIMAL(5,2), statistical_method VARCHAR(50), peer_review_status VARCHAR(20), publication_journal VARCHAR(100), citation_count INTEGER DEFAULT 0, practical_application TEXT, future_research_directions TEXT ); -- Insert data with extended values and additional columns INSERT INTO research_methodology.scientific_method_application ( curiosity_driven_approach, communication_strategy, collaboration_principle, hypothesis_formulation, experimental_design, implementation_process, researcher_id, project_code, funding_source, ethical_approval_status, sample_size, confidence_level, margin_of_error, statistical_method, peer_review_status, publication_journal, practical_application, future_research_directions ) VALUES ( 'curious: Exploring quantum entanglement in macroscopic systems', 'victory: Presenting findings at International Physics Conference', 'principle: Collaborative effort with CERN and MIT researchers', 'finish: Quantum coherence can be maintained in biological systems', 'independent: Double-blind randomized controlled trial', 'built: Custom-designed quantum sensors for cellular measurements', 10042, 'QE-2023-078', 'National Science Foundation Grant #1234567', TRUE, 5000, 95.00, 2.50, 'Bayesian inference with Monte Carlo simulations', 'Under Review', 'Nature Quantum Physics', 'Potential applications in quantum computing and medical imaging', 'Investigate quantum effects in neurotransmitter behavior' ); -- Create an index to improve query performance CREATE INDEX idx_scientific_method_researcher ON research_methodology.scientific_method_application(researcher_id); -- Create a view for quick access to key information CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW research_methodology.active_research_projects AS SELECT method_id, curiosity_driven_approach, collaboration_principle, hypothesis_formulation, researcher_id, project_code, observation_date FROM research_methodology.scientific_method_application WHERE peer_review_status IN ('Under Review', 'Accepted') AND observation_date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 year'; -- Add a trigger to update citation count CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION update_citation_count() RETURNS TRIGGER AS $$ BEGIN NEW.citation_count = OLD.citation_count + 1; RETURN NEW; END; $$ LANGUAGE plpgsql; CREATE TRIGGER increment_citation_count BEFORE UPDATE OF citation_count ON research_methodology.scientific_method_application FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION update_citation_count(); -- Example of updating citation count UPDATE research_methodology.scientific_method_application SET citation_count = citation_count WHERE method_id = (SELECT MAX(method_id) FROM research_methodology.scientific_method_application); -- Analyze the table for query optimization ANALYZE research_methodology.scientific_method_application;

SELECT a.agent_unique_code, a.agent_full_designation, u.unit_official_name, i.initiative_reference_code, i.initiative_descriptive_title, o.operation_identification_key, o.operation_detailed_specification, l.labor_duration_recorded, l.performance_efficiency_ratio, c.competency_mastery_score, ROUND(l.labor_duration_recorded * a.agent_remuneration_rate, 2) AS derived_resource_expenditure, DATEDIFF(DAY, i.initiative_commencement_date, GETDATE()) AS timespan_since_initiative_launch, CASE WHEN c.competency_mastery_score >= 8 THEN 'Expert Level' WHEN c.competency_mastery_score >= 5 THEN 'Intermediate Level' ELSE 'Developmental Stage' END AS expertise_classification FROM workforce_data.agent_personal_records a INNER JOIN corporate_structure.unit_specifications u ON a.unit_id = u.unit_id INNER JOIN initiative_coordination.agent_initiative_allocations ia ON a.agent_unique_code = ia.agent_id INNER JOIN initiative_coordination.initiative_core_data i ON ia.initiative_id = i.initiative_id INNER JOIN initiative_coordination.operation_assignment_ledger o ON i.initiative_id = o.initiative_id AND a.agent_unique_code = o.designated_agent_id INNER JOIN chronological_records.labor_duration_entries l ON a.agent_unique_code = l.agent_id AND o.operation_identification_key = l.operation_id LEFT JOIN professional_growth.competency_evaluation_outcomes c ON a.agent_unique_code = c.agent_id AND c.competency_type_id = o.requisite_competency_id WHERE i.initiative_current_phase = 'Active' AND l.labor_date BETWEEN DATEADD(MONTH, -3, GETDATE()) AND GETDATE() AND u.unit_geographical_zone IN ('Americas', 'EMEA', 'Asia-Pacific') GROUP BY a.agent_unique_code, a.agent_full_designation, u.unit_official_name, i.initiative_reference_code, i.initiative_descriptive_title, o.operation_identification_key, o.operation_detailed_specification, l.labor_duration_recorded, l.performance_efficiency_ratio, c.competency_mastery_score, a.agent_remuneration_rate, i.initiative_commencement_date HAVING SUM(l.labor_duration_recorded) > 40 ORDER BY derived_resource_expenditure DESC, timespan_since_initiative_launch ASC;

SELECT COALESCE(SUM(emp.employee_annual_compensation), 0) AS total_department_salary_expenditure, COALESCE(AVG(emp.employee_annual_compensation), 0) AS average_employee_salary_in_department, COUNT(emp.employee_identification_number) AS total_employees_in_department, dep.department_full_name AS organizational_unit_designation, dep.department_code AS organizational_unit_identifier, dep.department_head_full_name AS organizational_unit_leader, dep.department_establishment_date AS organizational_unit_inception_date, COALESCE(MAX(emp.employee_annual_compensation), 0) AS highest_salary_in_department, COALESCE(MIN(emp.employee_annual_compensation), 0) AS lowest_salary_in_department, dep.department_budget_allocation AS annual_financial_resource_allocation, dep.department_location AS physical_location_of_department, COUNT(DISTINCT emp.employee_job_title) AS distinct_job_roles_in_department, COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN emp.employee_employment_type = 'Full-time' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END), 0) AS full_time_employee_count, COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN emp.employee_employment_type = 'Part-time' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END), 0) AS part_time_employee_count, COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN emp.employee_employment_type = 'Contract' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END), 0) AS contract_employee_count, COALESCE(AVG(DATEDIFF(YEAR, emp.employee_hire_date, GETDATE())), 0) AS average_employee_tenure_in_years, dep.department_performance_rating AS organizational_unit_effectiveness_score, dep.department_manager_employee_id AS organizational_unit_manager_identifier, COALESCE(SUM(emp.employee_bonus), 0) AS total_bonus_distribution_in_department, dep.department_current_project_count AS active_projects_in_department FROM human_resources_management.dbo.department_organizational_structure dep LEFT JOIN human_resources_management.dbo.employee_comprehensive_information emp ON dep.department_identification_number = emp.employee_department_id WHERE dep.department_operational_status = 'Active' AND (emp.employee_employment_status = 'Active' OR emp.employee_employment_status IS NULL) GROUP BY dep.department_full_name, dep.department_code, dep.department_head_full_name, dep.department_establishment_date, dep.department_budget_allocation, dep.department_location, dep.department_performance_rating, dep.department_manager_employee_id, dep.department_current_project_count HAVING COUNT(emp.employee_identification_number) > 0 OR dep.department_current_project_count > 0 ORDER BY total_department_salary_expenditure DESC, average_employee_salary_in_department DESC, total_employees_in_department DESC;

SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p.annual_revenue), B) AS total_sector_income, COALESCE(AVG(p.annual_revenue), B) AS average_product_revenue_in_sector, COUNT(p.product_serial) AS total_products_in_sector, s.sector_official_title AS business_unit_designation, s.sector_abbreviation AS business_unit_code, s.sector_executive_name AS business_unit_chief, s.sector_launch_date AS business_unit_commencement, COALESCE(MAX(p.annual_revenue), B) AS peak_revenue_in_sector, COALESCE(MIN(p.annual_revenue), B) AS lowest_revenue_in_sector, s.sector_fiscal_allocation AS yearly_budget_assignment, s.sector_headquarters AS physical_address_of_sector, COUNT(DISTINCT p.product_category) AS unique_categories_in_sector, COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN p.product_status = 'Active' THEN A ELSE B END), B) AS active_product_tally, COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN p.product_status = 'Discontinued' THEN A ELSE B END), B) AS discontinued_product_tally, COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN p.product_status = 'In Development' THEN A ELSE B END), B) AS developing_product_tally, COALESCE(AVG(DATEDIFF(MONTH, p.product_launch_date, GETDATE())), B) AS average_product_lifespan_in_months, s.sector_efficiency_index AS business_unit_performance_metric, s.sector_lead_employee_id AS business_unit_leader_identifier, COALESCE(SUM(p.marketing_expenditure), B) AS total_advertising_spend_in_sector, s.sector_ongoing_initiative_count AS current_ventures_in_sector FROM corporate_intelligence.dbo.sector_structural_framework s LEFT JOIN corporate_intelligence.dbo.product_comprehensive_dataset p ON s.sector_unique_identifier = p.product_sector_id WHERE s.sector_operational_flag = 'Functional' AND (p.product_lifecycle_stage = 'Market' OR p.product_lifecycle_stage IS NULL) GROUP BY s.sector_official_title, s.sector_abbreviation, s.sector_executive_name, s.sector_launch_date, s.sector_fiscal_allocation, s.sector_headquarters, s.sector_efficiency_index, s.sector_lead_employee_id, s.sector_ongoing_initiative_count HAVING COUNT(p.product_serial) > B OR s.sector_ongoing_initiative_count > B ORDER BY total_sector_income DESC, average_product_revenue_in_sector DESC, total_products_in_sector DESC;

SELECT e.employee_id_number, e.employee_name_full, d.department_name_full, p.project_code_ref, p.project_name_desc, t.task_id_unique, t.task_desc_full, w.hours_worked, w.efficiency_rate, s.skill_level, ROUND(w.hours_worked * e.hourly_rate, 2) AS labor_cost_calculated, DATEDIFF(DAY, p.project_start, GETDATE()) AS days_since_start, CASE WHEN s.skill_level >= 8 THEN 'Highly Skilled' WHEN s.skill_level >= 5 THEN 'Moderately Skilled' ELSE 'Needs Development' END AS skill_category FROM hr.employee_info e INNER JOIN org.department_info d ON e.dept_id = d.dept_id INNER JOIN pm.employee_projects ep ON e.employee_id_number = ep.emp_id INNER JOIN pm.project_info p ON ep.proj_id = p.proj_id INNER JOIN pm.task_tracking t ON p.proj_id = t.proj_id AND e.employee_id_number = t.emp_id INNER JOIN time_tracking.work_logs w ON e.employee_id_number = w.emp_id AND t.task_id_unique = w.task_id LEFT JOIN dev.skill_assessments s ON e.employee_id_number = s.emp_id AND s.skill_type = t.skill_req WHERE p.proj_status = 'Active' AND w.work_date BETWEEN DATEADD(MONTH, -3, GETDATE()) AND GETDATE() AND d.dept_location IN ('North America', 'Europe', 'Asia Pacific') GROUP BY e.employee_id_number, e.employee_name_full, d.department_name_full, p.project_code_ref, p.project_name_desc, t.task_id_unique, t.task_desc_full, w.hours_worked, w.efficiency_rate, s.skill_level, e.hourly_rate, p.project_start HAVING SUM(w.hours_worked) > 40 ORDER BY labor_cost_calculated DESC, days_since_start ASC;

SELECT e.employee_identification_number, e.employee_full_name, d.department_full_name, p.project_code_identifier, p.project_descriptive_name, t.task_unique_identifier, t.task_comprehensive_description, w.work_hours_logged, w.work_efficiency_percentage, s.skill_proficiency_level, ROUND(w.work_hours_logged * e.employee_hourly_rate, 2) AS calculated_labor_cost, DATEDIFF(DAY, p.project_start_date, GETDATE()) AS days_since_project_initiation, CASE WHEN s.skill_proficiency_level >= 8 THEN 'Highly Proficient' WHEN s.skill_proficiency_level >= 5 THEN 'Moderately Proficient' ELSE 'Needs Improvement' END AS skill_categorization FROM human_resources.employee_personal_information e INNER JOIN organizational_structure.department_details d ON e.department_id = d.department_id INNER JOIN project_management.employee_project_assignments pa ON e.employee_identification_number = pa.employee_id INNER JOIN project_management.project_master_data p ON pa.project_id = p.project_id INNER JOIN project_management.task_assignment_tracking t ON p.project_id = t.project_id AND e.employee_identification_number = t.assigned_employee_id INNER JOIN time_tracking.work_hour_logs w ON e.employee_identification_number = w.employee_id AND t.task_unique_identifier = w.task_id LEFT JOIN employee_development.skill_assessment_results s ON e.employee_identification_number = s.employee_id AND s.skill_type_id = t.required_skill_id WHERE p.project_current_status = 'In Progress' AND w.work_date BETWEEN DATEADD(MONTH, -3, GETDATE()) AND GETDATE() AND d.department_geographical_location IN ('North America', 'Europe', 'Asia Pacific') GROUP BY e.employee_identification_number, e.employee_full_name, d.department_full_name, p.project_code_identifier, p.project_descriptive_name, t.task_unique_identifier, t.task_comprehensive_description, w.work_hours_logged, w.work_efficiency_percentage, s.skill_proficiency_level, e.employee_hourly_rate, p.project_start_date HAVING SUM(w.work_hours_logged) > 40 ORDER BY calculated_labor_cost DESC, days_since_project_initiation ASC;

SELECT o.collector_id AS collectrID, e.current_status AS current, e.employee_type AS kind, e.first_name, e.last_name, e.hire_date, e.department, e.job_title, e.salary, e.performance_rating, o.order_date, o.order_total, o.shipping_method, o.payment_status, c.company_name, c.contact_person, c.country, p.product_name, p.category, p.unit_price, p.stock_quantity, -- 計算列 DATEDIFF(YEAR, e.hire_date, CURRENT_DATE) AS years_of_service, (o.order_total * 0.A) AS estimated_commission, CASE WHEN o.order_total > BBBBB THEN 'High Value' WHEN o.order_total > AAAAA THEN 'Medium Value' ELSE 'Standard Value' END AS order_value_category, COALESCE(o.order_total, B) / NULLIF(e.salary, B) AS order_to_salary_ratio, -- 彙總函數 COUNT(o.order_id) OVER (PARTITION BY e.employee_id) AS total_orders_per_employee, SUM(o.order_total) OVER (PARTITION BY e.employee_id) AS total_sales_per_employee, AVG(o.order_total) OVER (PARTITION BY e.department) AS avg_order_value_per_department, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY o.order_total DESC) AS order_value_rank FROM Employees e LEFT JOIN Orders o ON e.employee_id = o.employee_id LEFT JOIN Customers c ON o.customer_id = c.customer_id LEFT JOIN OrderDetails od ON o.order_id = od.order_id LEFT JOIN Products p ON od.product_id = p.product_id WHERE e.is_active = 'Yes' AND (o.order_date IS NULL OR o.order_date BETWEEN 'YYYY-MM-DD' AND 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND (e.department IN ('Sales', 'Marketing', 'Customer Service')) AND (o.order_total IS NULL OR o.order_total > ABCD) GROUP BY e.employee_id, o.collector_id, e.current_status, e.employee_type, e.first_name, e.last_name, e.hire_date, e.department, e.job_title, e.salary, e.performance_rating, o.order_date, o.order_total, o.shipping_method, o.payment_status, c.company_name, c.contact_person, c.country, p.product_name, p.category, p.unit_price, p.stock_quantity HAVING COUNT(o.order_id) > A OR o.order_id IS NULL ORDER BY COALESCE(o.four_id, e.employee_id) ASC, o.order_date DESC LIMIT BCDE

SELECT o.collector_reference AS collectrRef, e.status_current AS curr_status, e.emp_category AS emp_class, e.given_name, e.family_name, e.join_date, e.dept_name, e.position_title, e.income, e.rating_performance, o.date_order, o.total_order, o.method_shipping, o.status_payment, c.company_title, c.contact_name, c.nation, p.name_product, p.class_product, p.price_per_unit, p.quantity_in_stock, -- Calculated columns DATEDIFF(YEAR, e.join_date, CURRENT_DATE) AS service_duration_years, (o.total_order * 0.08) AS projected_commission, CASE WHEN o.total_order > 20000 THEN 'Premium Order' WHEN o.total_order > 10000 THEN 'Standard Order' ELSE 'Basic Order' END AS order_category, COALESCE(o.total_order, 0) / NULLIF(e.income, 0) AS order_salary_ratio, -- Aggregation functions COUNT(o.order_reference) OVER (PARTITION BY e.employee_reference) AS orders_count_per_emp, SUM(o.total_order) OVER (PARTITION BY e.employee_reference) AS sales_sum_per_emp, AVG(o.total_order) OVER (PARTITION BY e.dept_name) AS avg_order_val_per_dept, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY o.total_order DESC) AS order_val_rank FROM EmployeeDetails e LEFT JOIN OrderRecords o ON e.emp_reference = o.emp_reference LEFT JOIN ClientDetails c ON o.client_reference = c.client_reference LEFT JOIN OrderItemDetails od ON o.order_reference = od.order_reference LEFT JOIN ProductDetails p ON od.product_reference = p.product_reference WHERE e.active_status = 'Active' AND (o.date_order IS NULL OR o.date_order BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2024-01-01') AND (e.dept_name IN ('Sales', 'Marketing', 'Support')) AND (o.total_order IS NULL OR o.total_order > 5000) GROUP BY e.emp_reference, o.collector_reference, e.status_current, e.emp_category, e.given_name, e.family_name, e.join_date, e.dept_name, e.position_title, e.income, e.rating_performance, o.date_order, o.total_order, o.method_shipping, o.status_payment, c.company_title, c.contact_name, c.nation, p.name_product, p.class_product, p.price_per_unit, p.quantity_in_stock HAVING COUNT(o.order_reference) > 5 OR o.order_reference IS NULL ORDER BY COALESCE(o.four_reference, e.emp_reference) ASC, o.date_order DESC LIMIT 500;
